Descriptions: Man with blue hat and white shirt throws a red frisbee towards two women who are sitting down and ready to receive the frisbee. Looks like they are outside the Ucen near the lagoon.
Guy looks at a woman who is getting out of a white car. They are looking at eachother, he is posed interestingly, like they are talking, or maybe they know eachother and want to say hi.
Man is holding a coffee cup, and something in his right hand. He is sitting at a low table in a dorm or apartment with other items on it.
A man dispenses tape from a clear tape dispenser, he is sitting at a low table in a dorm, with colorful objects on the table.
A student in a dorm is about to open a toothpaste tube. He is standing at a sink with sink related objects on it.
A person with large feet puts one foot up on a table in a dorm. There are two white socks that look far too small for them on the table.
A man uses a lighter to create a flame. There is a candle nearby so he is probably about to light it. He is also in a dorm, at a low table.
A person holds a damp paper towel at a low table in a dorm. There is a bowl to their left, and other items to their right.
A student bends over, probably tired, with two very heavy dumbbells at their feet. They just finished working out. They are in the common area of a dorm. There is a guitar in the corner.

Three people share a tangerine. One blonde woman with a red top is already enjoying a slice, while the man on the right hands the rest of the tangerine to another man to the left. They are at a park bench table.
A student reads the instructions to a jenga game, or similar game involving wooden blocks. They are sitting at a low table in a dorm with objects on the table.
Outside on the lawn of the ucsb library a man in a red shirt cheers on two sprinting women who are running past.
Two men outside the ucen by the lagoon watch as a women with a broom uses the handle end to poke at something in a young tree. One man was sitting, the other was standing.
A student paints their nails in a dorm with a low table. There is a cup to their left.
A student irons their plaid shirt in a dorm with a low table.
A sad or tired looking student holds their head in their hands while sitting in a messy looking dorm room, with a chess set in front of them. Perhaps he just lost a game of chess.
A unfortunate fellow just hurt his foot or toe with a hammer while trying to do something in his kitchen. He is yelling in pain.
A student puts on their white shoes over black long socks in a dorm room. There is a guitar in the corner. The room is pretty messy.
At a low black table, a student holds some food items. There is a large chef's knife, an apple, and some salt and pepper seasoning shakers on the table. It is an odd place to cook.
